title: Various Artists - Indie 69 Nov 2013 New Music Monthly
description:
November has arrived again already. And I will say again that it has
happened quickly, when in fact it has happened most likely at the same rate
as always. I assume.

This is a good month. I did not have as much time to prepare, but I think it 
turned out great anyway. Best of the year is on the way soon (I KNOW.. right?
already??!!) and it is SPECTACULAR!

Enjoy and yes, I will see you in a couple of weeks for best of the year AND
in DEC. Thanks for a fun year with a TON of incredible music.
